                 "- **Keyword Search (Sparse Retrieval)**: Uses statistical term frequencies (like BM25) to match exact character tokens. Best for searching specific product codes, serial numbers, names, or rare technical terms (e.g., finding 'ERR-90812' or 'SQLServer2022').\n\n"
